<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV22">
<l>paṇṭumiṉṟu mēlumāyor pālaṉāki ñālamē</l>
<l>ḻuṇṭumaṇṭi yālilaittu yiṉṟavāti tēvaṉē</l>
<l>vaṇṭukiṇṭu taṇṭuḻāya laṅkalāyka lantacīrp</l>
<l>puṇṭarīkap pāvaicēru mārpapūmi nātaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O primordial Lord who, becoming an infant, slept on the banyan leaf</l>
<l>having thrust in and swallowed the seven worlds [protecting] then, now, and further!</l>
<l>O You with a garland of cool tulasi poked by bees!</l>
<l>O You whose chest is joined by the Damsel on the excellent lotus! O Lord of the Earth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
